Author: Kathie Trapkin
Body: I can't log in to the app or the website. I got an email saying that I need to update my ID, but I can't log in because the app AND the website won't send me a text for 2-factor ID. There is no help, and I assume at this point that my money is inaccessible. The joke of a Help section seems to enjoy blaming my phone for not getting texts, but truth is that I'm texting other people as I wait for the text. No other option available - like send it to my friggin email on file!
